data.description: SUPER PRICE!! Looking for a solid home in Bogalusa that ticks all the boxes? This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom house offers practical living spaces without the frills. With 4 bedrooms, you've got options: home office, guest room, or a bit of extra storage. The layout is straightforward and user-friendly. The kitchen is equipped for day-to-day cooking. It's a functional space that can handle everything from microwave meals to one-pot dinners. The fenced backyard is more than adequate for pets or a small garden. You'll also find 2 sheds for your outdoor storage needs and a covered patio that offers shelter for your outdoor activities. This Bogalusa home is about value and practicality. Schedule a viewing to see if it's the right fit for you.
